data.name: Fish Sonar
data.desc: Add 1 Level 7 or lower monster that is a WATER Normal Monster or specifically lists "Umi" in its text from your Deck to your hand, then, if "Umi" is on the field, you can Special Summon 1 WATER Normal Monster from your Deck. You can only activate 1 "Fish Sonar" per turn.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Duelists: Duels From the Deep
